<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/19765730">什么是美？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="86357" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">最好能追溯美学（Aesthetica）的简要发展，以及中外知名理论家对美的论述的发展变迁史。</div>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-meta zm-item-comment-el clearfix" id="zh-question-meta-wrap">
<div class="zm-meta-panel">

